parameters:
\n<Yuuki>Congratulations on clearing the game! And thank
you for playing this far!

\n<Yuuki>This is a special little room just for the
NormalEND.

\n<Yuuki>It's kind of a breather spot without any hidden
elements, huh? If you want to go to the
recollection room, please head down to the
entrance below.

\n<Yuuki>But since you've made it this far... would you
like to hear how to reach the True End?

The condition for the True End is hidden in the
Rabbit House.

\n<To Begin With>You need to encounter a girl who is being raped.
The girl is located at the back of the lower left
passage of the dance floor.

\n<To Begin With>If Rui's resistance value is 2 or less, the men
raping the girl will disappear. First, let Rui get
to know the girl.

\n<Acquired The Aphrodisiac!>Talk to the customer who's run out of cigarettes
under the boob-loving old man at the bottom right
of the bar floor where the bartender is,

\n<Acquired The Aphrodisiac!>then obtain the electronic device placed on the
glass table at the bottom left of the dance floor
toilet, give it to a man on the bar floor, and get
an aphrodisiac.

\n<Acquired The Detoxifier!>Continue to the play floor on the right side of
the bar floor and give the aphrodisiac to a man
who looks like he's about to die from pulling out
too much, and in return, you'll receive a
detoxifier.

\n<Obtain Water>Return to the dressing room where you can change
clothes and obtain water from the refrigerator.

\n<Save The Girl>With Rui's resistance at 2 or below and when the
girl is alone, make her drink the detoxifier and
water you've obtained.

\n<Acquire The Vd Terminal>Once the girl regains consciousness, acquire a
terminal from the VD Room at the bottom right of
the VIP floor.

\n<To The World Caught In A Bug>Go to the Virtual Dive space and meet a certain
person to let Rui know "something important."

It's been a long explanation, but that's all.
Please check it out if you have time.

\n<Yuuki>I see! Once again, thank you so much for playing
this far!

Would you like to head to the Reminiscence
Room?※\C[10]The Reminiscence Room is a timeline
where Rui has been defeated by Tuberose.\C[10] The
corruption level of the lewd crest will forcibly
become 100.
